1、手动添加到注册表 win+R：regedit，HKEY_CLASSES_ROOT/SystemFileAssociations，右键单击SystemFileAssociations，添加项.py，右键单击.py，添加shell，继续如上操作，形成.py/shell/editwithidle/shell/edit36/command 在editwithidle处有MUIVerb&mdash;&amp;Edit with IDLE，Subcommands 在edit37处有MUIVerb&mdash;Edit with IDLE 3.7（64-bit） 在command处有数据&quot;C:\Users\Administrator\AppData\Local\Programs\Python\Python37\pythonw.exe&rdquo; -m idlelib &ldquo;%L&rdquo; %*  2、使用命令  Windows Registry Editor Version 5.00
[HKEY_CLASSES_ROOT\Python.File]
[HKEY_CLASSES_ROOT\Python.File\Shell]
[HKEY_CLASSES_ROOT\Python.File\Shell\editwithidle]&ldquo;MUIVerb&quot;=&rdquo;&amp;Edit with IDLE&quot;&ldquo;Subcommands&quot;=&rdquo;&rdquo;
[HKEY_CLASSES_ROOT\Python.File\Shell\editwithidle\shell]
[HKEY_CLASSES_ROOT\Python.File\Shell\editwithidle\shell\edit36]&ldquo;MUIVerb&quot;=&quot;Edit with IDLE 3.6 (64-bit)&rdquo;
[HKEY_CLASSES_ROOT\Python.File\Shell\editwithidle\shell\edit36\command]@=&rdquo;&quot;C:\Program Files\Python36\pythonw.exe&quot; -m idlelib &quot;%L&quot; %*&rdquo;
需要修改最后的文件目录！！！
  保存为py.reg（文件名随便），保存为所有文件，打开文件，注册成功即可。
  Reference https://jingyan.baidu.com/article/c1a3101e13087ade656deb83.html
